These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, epic
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, badminton
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, boat
1. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
2. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
3. the person watching epic movies is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate  | soy-milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic     | superhero   |
| Sport         | badminton | water-polo |
| Transport     | trike | boat    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: grapefruit, eggplant
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, time-travel
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, cat
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, trike
1. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching adventure movies is the person driving the trike##1
3. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | grapefruit     | eggplant |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | adventure  |
| Pet           | cat         | goldfish     |
| Transport     | roller   | trike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
