The people have 2 different jobs:  paramedic, architect
2 different pets are kept: turtle, goat
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the architect##3
2. the owner of the goat is on the right of the architect##1
3. the person drinking water is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | almond-milk     | water |
| Job         | architect | paramedic    |
| Pet         | turtle         | goat        |
| Transport   | tram         | taxi    |

